Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.14,0:00:10.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.54,0:00:12.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Anyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.96,0:00:19.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.16,0:00:23.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'll be your leg.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.01,0:00:25.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My leg?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.81,0:00:29.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'll make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.77,0:00:37.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,TL,[missing]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.61,0:00:49.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, you silly old bear...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,TL,[missing]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.91,0:01:03.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,As a Humanoid, serving her master is her top priority.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.53,0:01:07.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'd miss you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But if it would make you happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.29,0:01:13.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.19,0:01:15.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,it's pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.50,0:01:22.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri's more than just a Humanoid...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.53,0:01:24.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.25,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.46,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,{\an8}Awfully hot tea you got here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.46,0:03:14.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're lucky Natsuki-san even let you in here in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I hope you appreciate that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Someone attack you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.56,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.31,0:03:25.25,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san! My sensors are detecting alcohol!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You fell into the ocean in a drunken stupor?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.98,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up! Ain't nobody can handle life without a little booze!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.24,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I tell ya hwat, there's only two types of people in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.87,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,People what drink, and people what don't drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.87,0:03:44.37,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,And people what're none of the above!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.37,Alt,Atri,0,0,0,,That's three...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I see logic isn't on the menu tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.29,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Shaddap! Don't you be smart with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.17,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Times like this, you just go,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.01,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,"Oh, okay, you're so smart," capisce!?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, you're {\i1}so{\i0} smart.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.50,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Put a little enthusiasm into it, why don't you!?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.30,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You don't know a damn thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri, you deal with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Dun wanna.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.76,0:04:08.90,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Oh, nobody even cares about me anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.27,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Lord knows you're never selling the robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.33,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Then I just get to sit here waiting to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's really that bad?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.04,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Work as a private eye long enough,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.94,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,and you start brushing up against the seedy underbelly of society.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.23,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I've got no money.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.96,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You can guess the rest, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Even though you used to be a teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.13,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A very stupid private eye told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.93,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.58,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I was wondering where that went! You rotten thief!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're lucky I didn't loot it and chuck it into the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.31,0:04:47.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You should be thank-
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is that the debt collectors?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.02,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,How should I know!?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I didn't think they were this viol-
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.49,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I'll be a decoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.04,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You take that chance to run for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri, you go with Catherine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.73,0:05:15.50,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can't afford to leave your-
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You can't move to your full potential if you're stuck with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Go with Catherine and take out our enemies!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.90,Default,Man B,0,0,0,,Welp, let's go pick up the goods.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.84,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,All we're after is the Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.32,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,Push comes to shove...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.15,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.49,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Step one, we go to that storage container over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.41,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.33,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.23,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,After it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.93,Default,Man B,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.39,0:05:54.92,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,{missing}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.01,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's naptime for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.99,Default,Man A,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.44,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Hop on!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.70,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,They're after you! We have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.32,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.32,0:06:23.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san told me to take out our enemies!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.24,Default,Man C,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.39,Default,Man C,0,0,0,,We lost 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.39,0:06:30.45,Default,Junker,0,0,0,,All we can do now is see if we can loot the place for parts and-
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.75,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I hope you know what you're doing!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.70,Default,Junker,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.38,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You ain't going nowhere!
Comment: 10,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Rocket...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,65)}Rocket...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.70,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.57,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri! You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wait, you're the guy from the-
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.63,Default,Junker,0,0,0,,It wasn't my idea, I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.63,0:07:17.71,Default,Junker,0,0,0,,They said they'd reward me handsomely if I brought them the Humanoid!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.06,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,That doesn't change the fact that you attacked us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.06,0:07:26.47,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,The police may not be what they used to be, but with this much evidence,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.78,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I'll be impressed if they don't show you the inside of a cell!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.61,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Wait! We can talk this out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.99,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.03,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I'm always down for some quid pro quo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.99,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,{\frz344.6\pos(995.2,1029.6)}Hasta la vista!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.82,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,And don't come back, you got that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.45,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Sure wasn't expecting {\i1}that{\i0} to be how I paid back my debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.94,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,The world works in strange ways, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.94,0:08:03.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't want to ask for money, Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,He said he'd pay any price.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nothing good comes of getting too greedy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,the compensation I got was more than good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.57,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Welp, I'd better be going.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.57,0:08:20.86,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Sorry, and thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Going where?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.58,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I lost my bike, so not far.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.35,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I'll think about it on the road.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.35,0:08:29.82,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Oh, and this is for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.03,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,A little something to make up for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Keep it. You need the money, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.67,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Not any more than you do, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.57,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Shut up and let me save face.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.27,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't you want to come back here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.26,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.14,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You know I can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.62,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I abandoned this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.54,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I don't have a home anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's the school, isn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.16,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.61,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I saw the place.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.79,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Half the building's underwater.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.62,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,And all the teachers are gone, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But the school's still there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.85,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's almost time for class.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why don't you go see for yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.76,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Class?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're still having 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Got students here in need of an education, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The teacher isn't exactly qualified, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.70,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,School...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.23,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Okay, Ririka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Start reading from where we left off yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.53,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Mmkay.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.16,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,"Gon! So you were the one giving me chestnuts!"
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.95,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Gon nodded, his eyes still closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.20,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hyouju...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.29,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hana-chan-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.55,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,It's Hana-chan-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.57,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.75,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's you guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.21,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hana-chan-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.22,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,S-Stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.35,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,My name's Catherine now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.01,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Catherine?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Doesn't stick the landing, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Qu-Quiet, you! Catherine's a way cooler name!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.57,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.49,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,I really gotta question your taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.96,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I did some digging into your past.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.96,0:10:34.39,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I heard you were an incredible teacher,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.37,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,and everybody here loved you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.04,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Well, your info's dead wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I abandoned this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.35,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I still had students, but I took off and ran.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.79,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I couldn't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.67,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But you came back.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I love this city too much to give up on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.95,0:10:59.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I want to make it every bit as lively and bustling as it used to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.45,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,We don't have much at the moment...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.44,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But Hana-chan-sensei,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.09,0:11:09.73,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,will you please be everyone's teacher again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Come back to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.46,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hana-chan-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.19,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.99,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.44,0:11:23.32,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Stay away from me...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.19,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Sensei? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.67,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're catching the feels too, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.46,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.25,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We're gonna make that generator or die trying, got it!?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.25,0:11:43.34,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We're gonna light the school up and make it just like it used to be!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.70,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,And if we wanna do that, first, we need batteries.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.92,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We have to scrounge 'em up {\i1}somewhere{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, I got us some.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.65,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And I couldn't've done it without Hana-chan-sensei and Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.28,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You mean...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.64,0:12:00.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're gonna restore this school to its former glory.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.12,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Good grief, that's hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is gonna be harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.12,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,This'll take me a month, easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.01,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,If only I had an electric drill...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can you give it a try?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I just need to make a hole right here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Go for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.86,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You think she's got this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.94,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Sure, she's a Humanoid, but those spindly little arms-
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.86,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,All in a day's work for a combat robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.51,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Huh? You're a combat robot?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Source: her ass.
Comment: 10,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,[smug robot noises]
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.75,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Natsuki-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.75,Alt,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, give us more where that came from!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.01,Alt,Atri,0,0,0,,{\an8}You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're done?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.69,0:12:58.51,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,When we carved the styrofoam, it exploded and started snowing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wow, that came out pretty good.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.48,0:13:05.73,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Yeah! Hana-chan-sensei helped with the finishing touches!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.73,Alt,Catherine,0,0,0,,{\an8}Slow down!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did she, now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.14,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Wh-Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I just didn't want the kids to do it unsupervised...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.98,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Anyway, are you sure this is gonna work?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everything checks out in theory.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,First, we bust a hole in the floor
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,check timing,and cover the walls so water doesn't get into this room from outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,check timing,What happens at high tide, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.38,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Seawater comes in through the hole.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.38,0:13:31.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And of course, it leaves the same way at low tide.
Comment: 10,0:13:32.46,0:13:37.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Use that power to spin a turbine, and you've got a tidal power generator.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.46,0:13:37.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1019)}Use that power to spin a turbine, and you've got a tidal power generator.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.86,0:13:41.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The mechanism's really simple when you get down to it,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,so I think we have a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.33,0:13:47.98,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But I've heard waves can be pretty strong, can't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.22,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Sure they won't break anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.52,0:13:53.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The amount of seawater and the pressure it puts on the turbine aren't gonna be constant.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And the salt in the seawater opens up the possibility of corrosion.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's what makes tidal power generation tricky.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.49,0:14:02.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Long-term stability and replicability are paramount.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.11,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Stability?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.07,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.87,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,It means it needs to be sturdy as a rock.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.77,0:14:13.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And easy to rebuild when it breaks.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.90,0:14:17.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,In this classroom, we're gonna put resin and reinforced fibers together
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,to make FRP for our turbine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,FRP resists corrosion, and it's plenty strong for our purposes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.54,0:14:26.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And if it breaks, all you need is the model,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and you can make a replacement in no time flat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.06,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,So that's what...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sorry I gave you the annoying job.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But thanks to you, I think we're gonna have a great turbine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.21,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.75,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,But first, we'd better fill our bellies.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Let me know when you're done digging the hole.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'll be grabbing dinner upstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.95,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? You're going without me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.95,0:14:52.20,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah! Even an underling should get to eat with the rest of the gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm not an underling, but I agree with the rest of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you don't even need to eat, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.59,0:15:02.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Well, right now, I'm your leg, so I have to stay with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Relax. I'll be surrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.83,0:15:05.98,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I still want to go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,When we got attacked,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,and you ordered me to go with Catherine, I didn't like that, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I was worried sick that you'd get hurt while I was gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.50,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What's the harm?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.50,0:15:25.48,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to wait for the resin to harden anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,All right. Come with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.58,Default,Atir,0,0,0,,Yes! I'd love to!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.25,0:15:39.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So she feels unease and loneliness?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.22,0:15:44.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That basically means she's got all the same emotions a human does.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.34,0:15:49.55,Default,Fourth Generation,0,0,0,,And if that's why her generation was deemed too dangerous and recalled, then Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,is less a Humanoid, and more...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.23,Default,All,0,0,0,,Rub-a-dub-dub, thanks for the itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.53,Default,Ririka and Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.91,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've had rice from a mess kit, but this ain't half bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Great! Tooru-kun worked extra hard on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.55,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.55,0:16:12.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And we've got miso soup, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.98,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yippee! Look at all the ingredients!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.58,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Today's our lucky day!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And here's some for you, Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.22,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone else is eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.22,0:16:28.13,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You don't wanna feel left out, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.33,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.36,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Welp, time to take another whack at this thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.82,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,There's more where that came from!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ugh, you really gotta learn to do this yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm tired enough from working all day as it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.42,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Bu' hearly whi's'll hesh a higher hrishe...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Would you stop talking with your mouth open?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nice and clean!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.22,0:17:20.05,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Now this is beauty befitting my staggeringly high specs!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.05,0:17:20.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Will you wash my back, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can't reach it very well my-
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Awww! Why not!?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Because I said so!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.63,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're such a meanie, Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So she has no sense of shame, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.58,0:17:40.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Guess she's not {\i1}entirely{\i0} human...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.23,0:17:41.50,Alt,Atri,0,0,0,,{\an8}Natsuki-san! I'm turning off the lights!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I can think about this stuff tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you wearing that again!?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.46,0:18:00.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh, but Ryuuji said this is what men like.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm gonna deck him...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.48,0:18:04.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And this makes it easier for you catch some lucky glimpses,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.57,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,just like last time!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Y-{\alpha&HFF&}You noticed?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Y-You noticed?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course I noticed! My specs are out of this-
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Whatever! Just forget it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.14,0:18:20.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No way! I even recorded it in my logs!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Besides, it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It makes me feel like you need me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}Now you're just making stuff up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-Now you're just making stuff up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Freaking Roomba.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,So you compound your offenses, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.51,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Cease your racism at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I told you you had a rocket punch in your future if you kept it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.23,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,I checked the wiring. It's all good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri, you make sure it spins.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.95,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.54,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Does that mean we're making electricity?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.79,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.79,0:19:41.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Now we just wait for nighttime.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.21,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.21,0:19:52.01,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,It's spinning! It's spinning!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.30,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Wow... It's getting faster and faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Is this gonna turn on the lights?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Minamo, can you turn the knob?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.88,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think you should do the honors.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.88,0:20:05.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.29,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, turn the knob!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,TL,{\an8}[missing]
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.92,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.92,0:20:30.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.80,0:20:32.42,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.81,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.81,0:20:39.18,Default,Kids,0,0,0,TL,[missing]
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,When I came to this town,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I didn't want to come crawling back to my grandmother,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.21,0:20:56.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and I thought I had no future to look forward to now that I'd dropped out.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.80,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Can I go get a book to read?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.49,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,I wanna go see the fan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.83,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Don't trip and fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.27,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I can't believe you really pulled it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.79,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.08,0:21:14.59,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Thank you... Thank you for coming back...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.99,0:21:16.61,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Oh, don't cry...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.03,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You're such a baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I'm just so...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Same to you, Atri. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.68,0:21:29.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Can I take this to mean that everyone's happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You sure can. What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.45,0:21:39.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But I can't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't have the functionality.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But the robot I met there,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.49,0:21:54.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,the robot who'd been slumbering on the ocean floor for years,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.99,0:21:57.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,shone a light into my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And that robot...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then you can smile instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.84,0:22:02.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Smile?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.18,0:22:05.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.70,0:22:08.77,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yeah!
